<div class="b_title">  Expansion Scope of Accreditation</div>


<p class="marginBtm30">
In October 2020, GPC expanded the scope of auditor certification for 6 ISO management system standards through an accreditation audit from the accreditation body IAS.
</p>

<p class="marginBtm30">
Through GPC, you can acquire the auditor certification for the following standards.
</p>

<table border="1" color="#222" style="width:100%;margin: 20px 0 40px;">
<tbody>
<tr>
