<p class="marginBtm20">
In addition, according to the certification schemes developed by GPC, the following auditor certification services are provided.
</p>

<div class="marginBtm30">
<p class="list20">
- ISO 50001 Energy Management System
</p>
<p class="list20">
- ISO 37301 Compliance Management System
</p>
<p class="list20">
- ISO 22716 Cosmetics-Good Manufacturing Practices (CGMP)
</p>
<p class="list20">
- ISO/IEC 20000-1 Service Management System
</p>
<p class="list20">
- ISO 55001 Asset Management System
</p>
